{"tid":921440,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【獨家．揭爸爸身份】傳張栢芝與新加坡富豪誕男嬰","createTime":"2018-11-29T14:24:17.000Z","updateTime":"2018-11-29T14:33:37.000Z","uid":80516,"like":2,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"4e36b26bbd204b91ba7aa3abb9137d8644609642","tid":921440,"uid":80516,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-29T14:24:17.000Z","msg":"38歲張栢芝同謝霆鋒生咗2個仔Lucas同Quintus，2011年兩人離婚後，兩個仔由栢芝撫養，單身後嘅栢芝經常傳出新戀情，但冇一個會開花結果，但今年3月驚聞佢結識咗個年近60歲新加坡富豪，感情相當好，佢媽咪同弟弟張豪龍都好接受栢芝呢個新男友，有勸佢快啲公佈戀情。而今日有傳栢芝喺養和生咗第三胎，都係仔，傳經手人同爸爸就係呢位新加坡富豪。<br />\n<br />\n據可靠消息話孩子爸爸係新加坡連鎖飲食集團股東，其中仲有一間上市企業，身家雄厚。喺今年栢芝經常出入新加坡就係為咗同男友約會，有次佢帶男友去一個私人會所，咁啱嗰晚霆鋒都喺度，為免尷尬，栢芝後來帶男友換咗另一個地方。其實栢芝媽媽好幾個月前亮相節目時，佢提到栢芝新戀情，佢親口爆個女嘅男友係「一位65歲嘅新加坡富豪」，雖然年齡大栢芝27歲，但好會照顧人。<br />\n<br />\n今年3月初栢芝喺IG罕有貼出有男伴嘅游泳相。另外，佢今年2月底曾喺IG話過：「2018年之前必定要生出個BB來，This is my goal！」計番日子可能當時已經有咗，而發文後有網友問佢另一半是誰，當時佢同網民chitchat就回答：「圈外人不可以嗎！」<br />\n<br />\n栢芝同霆鋒分開後，其實都拍過唔少拖，好似同老外、大陸富豪孫東海、台灣主持何孟懷等都傳過緋聞，但好似都冇乜好結果，依家佢終於搵到真愛，仲肯為佢生小朋友，咁應該感情好好，之前栢芝情路崎嶇，希望佢以後可以真正幸福啦。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.entertainment.appledaily.com/enews/realtime/article/20181129/58973522\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.entertainment.appledaily.com%2Fenews%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20181129%2F58973522&d=2fkDh5FmsjrViBEEKUDa%2F8VakpCEQgWe3bOYm8oES40%3D&h=153b30ed\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.entertainment.appledaily.com%2Fenews%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20181129%2F58973522&h=62fe67de\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.entertainment.appledaily.com/enews/realtime/article/20181129/58973522</a>"},{"pid":"8561a2e0ea5db94d5889462d6c5297aef0a320ef","tid":921440,"uid":28765,"like":13,"dislike":0,"score":13,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-29T14:26:12.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"http://img.anyanother.com/data/73997.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fimg.anyanother.com%2Fdata%2F73997.jpg&h=37891031&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"c01114898d74bf76651a55d343638df640760d40","tid":921440,"uid":78349,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-29T14:27:01.000Z","msg":"點解十個月都冇人影到佢大肚<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"918f0235ad31862d8572cdcc0eb513aa0f80e714","tid":921440,"uid":12034,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-29T14:29:42.000Z","msg":"新加坡連鎖飲食集團<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n為左試鋒味可以去到幾盡"},{"pid":"3a7d723c7b13d3ec7850dffdf4f61c4e462745c5","tid":921440,"uid":61280,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-29T14:30:41.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: red;\">等睇三兄弟一比較，大佬同老三似冠A，二佬似四哥！！！！！<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span></strong></span></span>"},{"pid":"a31b8a68c9fd9efd6ec5931302091f86f80ef94a","tid":921440,"uid":49392,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-29T14:31:44.000Z","msg":"咁有錢都要食呢件，係愛呀屌你<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/wet.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/lick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"be7575edccbc4e5956ef8c61e37c34e9a19f5d80","tid":921440,"uid":21917,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-29T14:33:37.000Z","msg":"我估又係 生撚完就唔要<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}